Adding Year Slicer 13

Steps

Adding Year Slicer

·         Open Visualization pane

·         Select Slicer visual

·         Drag the visual to the dashboard.

·         Click on Calendar table and drag Year column from the Date Hierarchy then place it inside the field.

·         General: X - Position = 21, Y - Position = 93, Width = 200 and Height = 115; Move the year slicer and place it in between Project title and project logo.

 Slider Header = Off, Slider = On, Title = On, Title Text : Year -   Font Color : #FFFFF, Background Color : #00000,     Text Size : 17 and  Font family  : DIN, Alignment : center
